odybold\">- Fond et &Eacute;clisses en </span>Merisier<br /> <br /> <span class=\"mainbodybold\">- Manche en </span>&Eacute;rable Argent&eacute;<br /> <br /> <span class=\"mainbodybold\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Touche et chevalet en</span> Palissandre</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Sillet de T&ecirc;te  et Pont :</span> Compens&eacute; Tusq&reg; par Graphtech<span class=\"mainbodybold\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Largeur de Sillet de T&ecirc;te: </span>44mm (1.72\")</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Trussrod</span> Double Function <br /> <span class=\"mainbodybold\">&nbsp;</span><br /> <span class=\"mainbodybold\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Finition: </span>semi-lustr&eacute;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"mainbodybold\">- </span>Livr&eacute;e avec housse</p>',NULL,559,559,NULL,NULL,'10',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2613,11,'cr50-bk','CR50 BK',1,'<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Corps en Agathis</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Manche viss&eacute; en Erable argent&eacute; canadien</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Touche en Palissandre, 12\" Radius(305mm)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- 22 Frettes / Large (2.7mm)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Diapason 24 3/4\" (629mm)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Incrustations Point blanc</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- M&eacute;caniques Chrome&agrave; bain d\'huile</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Chevalet T.O.M.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Micros Powersound PSLP-1F et PSLP-1R (H-H)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Electronique: 1volume, 1 