th, o&ugrave; se trouve toujours la production principale des  guitares Martin.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">M&ecirc;lant  innovations et traditions, les guitares Martin repr&eacute;sentent une  v&eacute;ritable r&eacute;f&eacute;rence dans le monde de la guitare acoustique. L\'histoire  de la musique et l\'histoire de Martin sont si intimement li&eacute;es que le  son Martin fait partie de l\'histoire du blues, du rock, de la folk...</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />Gr&acirc;ce  &agrave; une gamme actuelle qui va de guitares abordables et innovatrices &agrave;  des reproductions de guitares vintage tout &agrave; fait exceptionnelles ; tout  le monde peut aujourd\'hui s\'offrir le son Martin et entrer dans la  grande famille des joueurs Martin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">CARACTERISTIQUES:</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />- Format Dreadnought 14  frettes hors corps</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Table massive en &eacute;pic&eacute;a de Sitka</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Fonds et &eacute;clisses  en HPL Acajou</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Barrage hybride en X all&eacute;g&eacute;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Pickguard motif &eacute;cailles de  tortue</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- M&eacute;caniques bain d\'huile</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Manche en stratabound</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- T&ecirc;te plaqu&eacute;e en  HPL Acajou</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Touche et chevalet en Richlite</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Nouveau profil de manche  Performing Artist</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Sillets en Corian</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Finition satin&eacute;e &agrave; la main</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Cutaway et syst&egrave;me amplifi&eacute; Fishman F1 Analog</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- Diapason de 64.5cm,  largeur au sillet 4.45cm</span></span></span></p>',NULL,1025,1025,NULL,NULL,'10',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3115,98,'rondelle-plate-pot-et-jack-usa-vr100','Rondelle Plate Pot. Et Jack USA VR100',1,'<h1>RONDELLE PLATE DE POTENTIOMETRES ET DE JACKS USA CH</h1>',NULL,0.25,0.25,NULL,NULL,'0',0,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(3116,271,'decimator','Decimator',1,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">P&eacute;dale de r&eacute;duction de bruit dans un chassis poli et chrom&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ISP  Technologies, l\'inventeur de la r&eacute;duction de bruit HUSH&reg; pr&eacute;sente avec  DECIMATOR la derni&egrave;re g&eacute;n&eacute;ration de r&eacute;duction de bruit en temps r&eacute;el. Le  syst&egrave;me HUSH et les autres syst&egrave;mes de r&eacute;duction de bruit ont tous un  gros probl&egrave;me :  ils ne peuvent pas r&eacute;pondre instantan&eacute;ment au staccato  tr&egrave;s brefs ni aux longues notes qui faiblissent lentement. Le syst&egrave;me  typique de r&eacute;duction de bruit souffre d\'une zone inactive dans sa  r&eacute;ponse, obligeant &agrave; un compromis lorsqu\'il suit des notes tr&egrave;s courtes  ou tr&egrave;s longues. La conception du Decimator offre une nouvelle approche  au suivi de l\'enveloppe du signal, appel&eacute;e Time Vector Processing  (traitement de vecteur temporel). Gr&acirc;ce &agrave; elle, le syst&egrave;me du Decimator  r&eacute;pondra imm&eacute;diatement aux note...</p>',NULL,173,173,NULL,NULL,'10',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3117,267,'orbit','Orbit',1,'<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;\">Avec  l\'Orbit dBucket, Strymon a assid&ucirc;ment reproduit les principaux aspects  des meilleurs Flanger analogiques vintages. Bien entendu, Strymon est  all&eacute; bien plus loin que cela en int&eacute;grant de nouvelles fonctions  in&eacute;dites telles que le mode Zero, une sortie p&eacute;dale d\'expression pour  commander en temps r&eacute;el n\'importe quel param&egrave;tre, un bouton \"favorite\"  pour sauvegarder un preset etc... Ajoutez &agrave; cela des sorties st&eacute;reo, le  true bypass, la finition en aluminium anodis&eacute; et la qualit&eacute; de  fabrication Strymon, vous obtenez un des meilleurs Flanger sur le  march&eacute;, qui nous en sommes s&ucirc;rs vous satisfera &agrave; 100%!</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic;\">Alimentation 9V fournie</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic;\"><br /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;\">CARACTERISTIQUES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><br /></span>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Hand crafted dBucket algorithm for highly accurate reproduction of every stage of an analog bucket brigade chip.</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Super low noise, high performance A/D and D/A converters w/ 110dB signal to noise</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- High performance DSP stuffed into a compact form factor</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- 3 LFO types (log, lin, through zero)</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- 3 Feedback types (positive, negative, pos/neg)</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- TRUE BYPASS (electromechanical relay switching)</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Stereo output</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Expression pedal input with selectable control over any knob parameter</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Favorite footswitch for saving your favorite setting</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Powered with a standard 9V center negative DC supply. Compatible with all major DC supply brands. Current consumption 250mA</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Premium analog front end and output section</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- No-nonsense user interface</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Strong and lightweight purple anodized aluminum chassis</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\">- Crafted in the USA</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;\"><br /></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<object width=\"560\" height=\"315\" data=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/nH8YixHDihg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\">\r\n<param name=\"data\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/nH8YixHDihg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" />\r\n<param name=\"src\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/nH8YixHDihg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>',NULL,355,355,NULL,NULL,'10',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3128,275,'subtle-volume-control','Subtle Volume Control',1,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Le SVC est un accessoire qui permet un meilleur  contr&ocirc;le du volume qu\'une p&eacute;dale de volume traditionnelle, car sa course  est plus grande et permet donc de modifier le volume sur des incr&eacute;ments  plus courts. Bien qu\'il soit con&ccedil;u pour &ecirc;tre branch&eacute; sur la boucle  d\'effet d\'un ampli (afin de ne pas modifier le gain r&eacute;gl&eacute; de celui-ci),  il marchera tout aussi bien plac&eacute; &agrave; la fin de votre cha&icirc;ne de p&eacute;dales  d\'effet (m&ecirc;me si votre gain sera alors affect&eacute; lui aussi).</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">R&eacute;glages : Volume.</span></p>',NULL,74,74,NULL,NULL,'10',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3130,53,'od9','OD9',1,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\'inventeur de la TS9 r&eacute;&eacute;dite son mod&egrave;le original en am&eacute;liorant la section de sortie pour att&eacute;nuer les bruits. <br />Enti&egrave;rement analogique et &eacute;quip&eacute;e des circuits JRC 4558 D, elle offre un grain unique. <br />Tout comme l\'OD-808, l\'OD-9 propose l\'overdrive naturelle et douce  d\'un ampli &agrave; lampes, sans sacrifier le grain original de votre guitare. <br />Utilisable comme booster sans alt&eacute;ration de signal. <br />&nbsp;<br />R&eacute;glages : Drive, Balance, Tone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<object width=\"560\" height=\"315\" data=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/EIM1aTcQHYg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\">\r\n<param name=\"data\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/EIM1aTcQHYg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" />\r\n<param name=\"src\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/EIM1aTcQHYg?version=3&amp;hl=fr_FR&amp;rel=0\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>',NULL,129,129,NULL,NULL,'10',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3133,277,'bb-preamp','BB Preamp',1,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Le BB Preamp est un boost clair allant jusqu\'&agrave; +30dB  et dot&eacute; d\'une &eacute;galisation active 2 bandes de +/-15dB. Elle utilise un  &eacute;tage pr&eacute;c&eacute;dant le gain et permet d\'aller d\'un son clair &eacute;clatant  jusqu\'&agrave; un overdrive compress&eacute; et tr&egrave;s doux. V&eacute;ritable bypass.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">R&eacute;glages : Gain, volume, treble, bass.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></p>\r