eacute;bit offre la bande passante n&eacute;cessaire pour une r&eacute;solution audio de 24-bit/96kHz en enregistrement et monitoring multipistes, avec une vitesse de transfert de donn&eacute;es de 480 Mbps.\">USB</dfn></strong></a> Audio<br />- EntreÌe MP3/Ligne<br />- Sortie simulateur de HP<br />- Alimentation externe incluse</p>',NULL,289,289,NULL,NULL,'10',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4652,203,'mecaniques-3x3-type-gibson-m3kcp1','MÃ©caniques 3x3 Type GIBSON M3KCP1',NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">M&eacute;caniques GOTOH SD90</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Boutons tulipe type Gibson</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Sans &eacute;crous</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3x3</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ratio 1:15</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nickel</span></p>',NULL,38,38,NULL,NULL,'0',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4653,203,'string-retainer-butterfly-bk-sr01b','String Retainer Butterfly BK SR01B',NULL,'<p>Prix pour 2 pi&egrave;ces</p>',NULL,7.199999809265137,7.19999980927,NULL,NULL,'0',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4654,203,'string-retainer-butterfly-gd-sr01g','String Retainer Butterfly GD SR01G',NULL,'<p>Prix pour 2 pi&egrave;ces</p>',NULL,7,7,NULL,NULL,'0',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4655,98,'roller-string-black-nt50b','Roller String Black NT50B',NULL,'<p>ROLLER STRING TREE BLACK + VIS (1 pi&egrave;ce)</p>',NULL,5,5,NULL,NULL,'0',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4656,98,'roller-string-gold-nt50g','Roller String Gold NT50G',NULL,'<p>ROLLER STRING TREE GOLD + VIS (1 pi&egrave;ce)</p>',NULL,5,5,NULL,NULL,'0',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4657,203,'string-retainer-cylindric-ck-sr02ck','String Retainer Cylindric CK SR02CK',NULL,'<p>Prix pour 2 pi&egrave;ces</p>',NULL,6.5,6.5,NULL,NULL,'0',1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4658,203,'string-retainer-cylindric-gd-sr02g','String Retainer Cylindric GD SR02G',NULL,'<p>Prix pour 