\"font-size: small;\">La position 25W en bas donne un crunch plein de r&eacute;ponse en fr&eacute;quence, similaire &agrave; l\'&eacute;tage de gain British du JCM800.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">La position 25W en haut part dans la distorsion avec des harmoniques riches, beaucoup de m&eacute;diums et une pr&eacute;sence incisive. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">La AT marche en 9v ou 18V pour plus dynamique et de r&eacute;ponse en fr&eacute;quence.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">R&eacute;glages : Volume, eq, drive, air, switch headroom (25w/50w/100w).</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>',NULL,259,259,NULL,NULL,'10',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(5187,383,'lampes-6v6s-duet-appairees','Lampes 6V6S Duet AppairÃ©es',NULL,'<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ensemble de 2 lampes de puissance appair&eacute;es</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 1;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Achetez nous les lampes, nous vous offrons la pose et le r&eacute;glage du BIAS!</span></strong></span></p>',NULL,50,50,NULL,NULL,'0',0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(5188,383,'lampes-el34-duet-appairees','Lampes EL34 Duet AppairÃ©es',NULL,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Lucida Grande\', \'Lucida Sans Unicode\', Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; orphans: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: small;\">Ensemble de 2 lampes de puissance appair&eacute;es</span></p>\r\n<p